Audited Financial Results (Standalone And Consolidated) Of The Company Prepared In Accordance With The IND-AS For The Quarter And Year Ended On March 31, 2021 Along With Audit Report Issued By The Auditors Of The Company And Declaration Pursuant To Regulation 33 (30) (D) Of The SEBI (LODR) Regulations, 2015 In Respect Of The Aforesaid Audited Financial Results
data.news_body: The Audited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) of the Company prepared in accordance with the IND-AS for the quarter and year ended on March 31, 2021 along with Audit Report issued by the Auditors of the Company and Declaration pursuant to Regulation 33 (30) (d) of the SEBI (LODR) Regulations, 2015 in respect of the aforesaid Audited Financial Results as approved in the Board Meeting held on June 28, 2021 are enclosed herewith in the Outcome of Board of Meeting.
